# Internship Project: Purple Team Automation Exploration

**Internship Project by Tony To**  
*Triskele Labs Internship Programme (Jan-Feb 2026)*

> **Note**: This is an educational project developed during an internship at 
> Triskele Labs. It demonstrates plugin development skills and security 
> automation concepts, but is NOT production software. All code is exploratory 
> and for portfolio demonstration purposes.

## Project Overview

This repository documents my exploration of Caldera plugin development during 
my internship at Triskele Labs. The project focuses on:

- Learning Caldera's plugin architecture through hands-on development
- Exploring ELK Stack integration patterns for security event correlation
- Practicing Python development in a security automation context
- Building a portfolio piece demonstrating security engineering skills

**This is NOT**:
- Production-ready software
- Official Triskele Labs intellectual property
- Intended for deployment in real environments
- A commercial product or service

